{"tid":1211023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日香港有如納粹？影帝忍無可忍齊砲轟","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T14:55:03.000Z","uid":202830,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4acffdbc032f98cf735887209155a17a11acab2a","tid":1211023,"uid":202830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"今日香港有如納粹？影帝忍無可忍齊砲轟<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/06YIBBg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F06YIBBg.jpg&h=2a9f8b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜汶澤（左）和黃秋生（右）均不滿港府攻擊民眾，在臉書貼文抨擊。<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中事件演變成流血衝突，香港知名演員杜汶澤、黃秋生等人也在臉書上痛批港府<br />\n；杜汶澤今（12）日批評香港警察是垃圾，並響應罷工運動；黃秋生則形容港府作為有如<br />\n德國納粹。<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤今在自己經營的媒體「喱騷Chapman To&rsquo;s late show」臉書發文痛批香港政府「<br />\n香港警察正一垃圾，本台予以強烈譴責」，並向76萬名收視觀眾指出，公司員工集體罷工<br />\n，要大家約三五好友去郊外野餐，並提醒最近香港天氣變化無常，請各位郊遊人士保重身<br />\n體。<br />\n<br />\n黃秋生今也在臉書發表看法，他貼出1張香港警察在地鐵站盤查民眾、搜索個人物品的照<br />\n片，再附上1張1933年德國納粹迫害猶太人的歷史照，在貼文中寫道：「Hello darkness<br />\nmy old friend（哈囉黑暗，我的老友）」，形容港府作為如同納粹般野蠻。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zEx7kt1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzEx7kt1.jpg&h=ecc533c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃秋生FB+截圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.com/264580710348010/photos/a.305882296217851/1469887933150609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2F264580710348010%2Fphotos%2Fa.305882296217851%2F1469887933150609&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=35ec8cb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/264580710348010/photos/a.305882296217851/1469887933150609</a><br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤FB截圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/m6MF8AI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fm6MF8AI.jpg&h=12924bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2820397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2820397&d=o1jNmZJj5m3DpFdm5BDgv72U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=87b6ebaf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2820397&h=e933b88f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2820397</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">感謝兩位出聲</span></span>"}]}